{{葡萄牙政治}}
'''2021年葡萄牙總統選舉'''於2021年1月24日（星期日）舉行，<ref>{{cite web|title=O Presidente da República, Marcelo Rebelo de Sousa, marcou hoje as eleições presidenciais para 24 de janeiro de 2021.|url=https://24.sapo.pt/atualidade/artigos/presidente-da-republica-marca-eleicoes-presidenciais-para-24-de-janeiro|website=www.24.sapo.pt|publisher=Sapo|access-date=2020-11-24|language=pt|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122030427/https://24.sapo.pt/atualidade/artigos/presidente-da-republica-marca-eleicoes-presidenciais-para-24-de-janeiro|dead-url=no}}</ref>共有7名候選人，包括爭取連任的[[馬塞洛·雷貝洛·德索薩|馬塞洛·雷貝洛·德索薩]]。<ref name="swissinfo01"/>

==選舉制度==
總統選舉採取[[两轮选举制|两轮选举制]]，設有[[早期投票|提早投票]]，於2021年1月17日舉行，有意提早投票的選民需預先登記。2021年總統選舉有246,880人登記提早投票，是2016年選舉的接近5倍<ref name="swissinfo01">{{cite web |url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%89%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F-%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%89%E6%B0%91%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E7%BA%AA%E5%BD%95/46295518 |title=封城之下选总统 葡萄牙提前投票选民创新纪录 |website=swissinfo.ch |date=2021-01-18 |access-date=2021-01-23 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130050708/https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%89%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F-%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%89%E6%B0%91%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E7%BA%AA%E5%BD%95/46295518 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://eco.sapo.pt/2021/01/16/portugueses-comecam-a-votar-nas-presidenciais-este-domingo-e-ha-246-mil-inscritos/ |title=Portugueses começam a votar nas Presidenciais este domingo e há 246 mil inscritos |work=Eco |date=2021-01-16 |accessdate=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116115144/https://eco.sapo.pt/2021/01/16/portugueses-comecam-a-votar-nas-presidenciais-este-domingo-e-ha-246-mil-inscritos/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有197,903人提早投票<ref>{{cite web |url=https://eco.sapo.pt/2021/01/21/80-dos-inscritos-votaram-no-domingo-para-as-presidenciais/ |title=80% dos inscritos votaram no domingo para as presidenciais |work=Eco |date=2021-01-21 |accessdate=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121104023/https://eco.sapo.pt/2021/01/21/80-dos-inscritos-votaram-no-domingo-para-as-presidenciais/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整体投票率下降了9个百分点，降至39.24％，这主要是由于海外选民的自动登记使登记选民的人数增加到近1100万<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tsf.pt/portugal/politica/recenseamento-automatico-de-emigrantes-fez-subir-abstencao-seis-pontos-13273900.html|title=Recenseamento automático de emigrantes fez subir abstenção seis pontos|publisher=TSF Radio|date=2021-01-25|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126102730/https://www.tsf.pt/portugal/politica/recenseamento-automatico-de-emigrantes-fez-subir-abstencao-seis-pontos-13273900.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。葡萄牙国内投票率为45.45％，与2016年选举相比下降了4.6个百分点，这是自1980年以来投票率的最低点。

==選舉結果==
現任總統[[馬塞洛·雷貝洛·德索薩|馬塞洛·雷貝洛·德索薩]]在首輪投票以得票率60.70%成功獲得連任<ref>{{Cite web|title=疫情肆虐下舉行大選 葡萄牙總統德索沙順利連任 - 國際|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210125002383-260408?chdtv|accessdate=2021-01-25|last=中時新聞網|work=中時新聞網|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131123526/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210125002383-260408?chdtv|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

